SUMMARY:Kids Comic Club
LOCATION:Kay Fox Room
URL:https://keenenh.libcal.com/event/16865804
CATEGORIES:kids\,Keene Public Library
DESCRIPTION:For comic fans ages 8-12! We'll meet once a month to create to
 gether\, discuss great graphic novels\, and watch interviews and tutorials
  from our favorite artists. All skill levels are welcome\, and materials w
 ill be provided! Meetings will be held on the second Friday of each month.
 \n\nRegistration is appreciated. Questions or Concerns call the library 60
 3.352.0157.\nSource: Keene Public Library
END:VEVENT
