BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:00bb456007fe61d4@kidcal
DTSTAMP:20260723T122613Z
DTSTART:20260930T143000Z
DTEND:20260930T151500Z
SUMMARY:Preschool Storytime
LOCATION:Storyroom
URL:https://keenenh.libcal.com/event/17090835
CATEGORIES:kids\,Keene Public Library
DESCRIPTION:Preschool storytimes are geared towards pre-kindergarteners ag
 es 3 to 5\, who can sit and listen to short stories and participate in sim
 ple songs and rhymes. Storytime will always include read-aloud stories and
  fingerplays and may include poems\, music\, dramatic play\, and crafts. \
 n\n \n\nThis is a 7-week series\, which ends the week of November 15th. Wh
 en you sign up for one class\, you will automatically be registered for ea
 ch class in the series.\n\nPLEASE NOTE: We will not meet on Wednesday Nove
 mber 11th in honor of Veterans Day. Our last meeting will be Wednesday Nov
 ember 18th.\nSource: Keene Public Library
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
