DTSTAMP:20260723T122613Z
DTSTART:20261001T143000Z
DTEND:20261001T151500Z
SUMMARY:Book time with Babies and Toddlers
LOCATION:Storyroom
URL:https://keenenh.libcal.com/event/17146447
CATEGORIES:kids\,Keene Public Library
DESCRIPTION:We'll share books\, rhymes\, music\, fun fingerplays\, puppets
 \, and get-up-and-move activities specially designed for infants and toddl
 ers. At the end of the program\, there will be a playtime when parents and
  caregivers share books\, puzzles\, or other early literacy activities wit
 h their toddlers.  This 7 week series ends the week of November 8th.  When
  you sign up for one class\, you will automatically be registered for each
  session in the series.\nSource: Keene Public Library
END:VEVENT
