DESCRIPTION:Weekly playgroup – fun activities\, games and a snack! Locat
 ion changes seasonally. Open to ages 0 – 6 and their siblings of any age
 . No need to register\, just show up! Email kayla.bapp@sapcc-vt.org for mo
 re information.\nSource: Springfield Area Parent Child Center
END:VEVENT
